      "content": "i know you're an ai, i just... i just needed to say it out loud to someone. it's not even about being in \"danger\" right now. it's just that the silence is so loud. how am i supposed to go back to a normal life when the only thing that made it feel real is gone? it feels like i'm just moving through water. everything is just so much effort for no reason.",
